TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT EDRAY_SHIPMENT_ID AS EDRAY_SHIPMENT_ID , MANIFEST_NUM AS MANIFEST_NUM , CONTAINER_NUM AS CONTAINER_NUM , MASTER_BL AS MASTER_BL , HOT_SHIPMENT_FLAG AS HOT_SHIPMENT_FLAG , CONTAINER_STATUS AS CONTAINER_STATUS , EQUIPMENT_TYPE AS EQUIPMENT_TYPE , VESSEL_NAME AS VESSEL_NAME , CAST(PORT_ARRIVAL_DATE_EST AS DATE) AS PORT_ARRIVAL_DATE_EST , CAST(PORT_ARRIVAL_DATE_ACTUAL AS DATE) AS PORT_ARRIVAL_DATE_ACTUAL, FINAL_CY_BL_DESTINATION AS FINAL_CY_BL_DESTINATION , DISCHARGE_PORT AS DISCHARGE_PORT , FINAL_DESTINATION AS FINAL_DESTINATION , CAST(CUSTOMS_ABI_RELEASE_DT AS DATE) AS CUSTOMS_ABI_RELEASE_DT , CAST(ASSIGN_DATE AS DATE) AS ASSIGN_DATE , CUSTOMER_REFERENCE AS CUSTOMER_REFERENCE , CUSTOMS_HOLD_STATUS AS CUSTOMS_HOLD_STATUS , LINE_STATUS AS LINE_STATUS , CAST(PORT_AVAILABLE_DATE AS DATE) AS PORT_AVAILABLE_DATE , CAST(PICK_UP_SCHEDULED_DATE AS DATE) AS PICK_UP_SCHEDULED_DATE , CAST(CONTAINER_OUT_GATE_DT AS DATE) AS CONTAINER_OUT_GATE_DT , CAST(LOADED_ON_RAIL_DT AS DATE) AS LOADED_ON_RAIL_DT , CAST(RAIL_ARRIVAL_INTERMODAL_DT AS DATE) AS RAIL_ARRIVAL_INTERMODAL_DT , CONTAINER_YARD_STATUS AS CONTAINER_YARD_STATUS , DC_DELIVERY AS DC_DELIVERY , TERMINAL AS TERMINAL , ETA_TO_DC AS ETA_TO_DC , INTERMODAL_CARRIER AS INTERMODAL_CARRIER , EMPTY_NOTIFY AS EMPTY_NOTIFY , EMPTY_RETURN AS EMPTY_RETURN, VALIDATED AS VALIDATED from STAGING.STG_EDRAY where CREATE_TIMESTAMP=TO_DATE('$$CREATE_TIMESTAMP','MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS') and processed_flag = 'N'

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Update Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: UPDATE MANIFEST_HEADER SET OCEAN_CARRIER_BILL_NBR = :TU.OCEAN_CARRIER_BILL_NBR, OCEAN_EQUIPMENT_NBR = :TU.OCEAN_EQUIPMENT_NBR, OCEAN_EQUIPMENT_TYPE = :TU.OCEAN_EQUIPMENT_TYPE, VESSEL_NAME = :TU.VESSEL_NAME, EST_DISCHARGE_PORT_ARRIVE_DT = :TU.EST_DISCHARGE_PORT_ARRIVE_DT, ACT_DISCHARGE_PORT_ARRIVE_DT = :TU.ACT_DISCHARGE_PORT_ARRIVE_DT, CUSTOMS_ABI_RELEASE_DT = :TU.CUSTOMS_ABI_RELEASE_DT, DELIVERY_ORDER_ISSUED_DT = :TU.DELIVERY_ORDER_ISSUED_DT, CONTAINER_OUTOFGATE_DT = :TU.CONTAINER_OUTOFGATE_DT, RAIL_LOADED_DT = :TU.RAIL_LOADED_DT, RAIL_ARRIVAL_AT_INTERMODAL_DT = :TU.RAIL_ARRIVAL_AT_INTERMODAL_DT, FINAL_DESTINATION_NAME = :TU.FINAL_DESTINATION_NAME, DC_DELIVERY_DT = :TU.DC_DELIVERY_DT, EDRAY_SHIPMENT_ID = :TU.EDRAY_SHIPMENT_ID, HOT_SHIPMENT_FLAG = :TU.HOT_SHIPMENT_FLAG, CONTAINER_STATUS = :TU.CONTAINER_STATUS, FINAL_CY_BL_DESTINATION = :TU.FINAL_CY_BL_DESTINATION, DISCHARGE_PORT = :TU.DISCHARGE_PORT, CUSTOMER_REFERENCE = :TU.CUSTOMER_REFERENCE, CUSTOMS_HOLD_STATUS = :TU.CUSTOMS_HOLD_STATUS, LINE_STATUS = :TU.LINE_STATUS, PORT_AVAILABLE_DATE = :TU.PORT_AVAILABLE_DATE, PICK_UP_SCHEDULED_DATE = :TU.PICK_UP_SCHEDULED_DATE, CONTAINER_YARD_STATUS = :TU.CONTAINER_YARD_STATUS, TERMINAL = :TU.TERMINAL, ETA_TO_DC = :TU.ETA_TO_DC, INTERMODAL_CARRIER = :TU.INTERMODAL_CARRIER, EMPTY_NOTIFY = :TU.EMPTY_NOTIFY, EMPTY_RETURN = :TU.EMPTY_RETURN, VALIDATED = :TU.VALIDATED WHERE MANIFEST_NBR = :TU.MANIFEST_NBR
